replies.body:
Hey Riot Swimbananas, I think this show would be great with a co-host. It seems a little odd when it's only you presenting everything. If you had one more person I believe you would be able to make the show a lot more engaging and it would allow for dialogue, instead of a monologue. I love your personality, however, the show needs diversity in order to showcase the vast diversity among League players.

Love the show, keep up the great work!
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
